Rating: 4
Excellent! Quick, easy, and tasty. I love that it can be made quickly with ingredients on hand. I have yet to make it in an 8" pan, but have made it countless times in small ramekins for individual-sized desserts. I've made the recipe as-is, but prefer it less sweet, so I cut the sugar back to 2Tbsp and it's perfect. Love it with ice cream, but have also topped it with a smear of whipped cream cheese and a fresh-made berry (cherry or raspberry) compote for an extra-luxe treat. Delish!

