Like other reviewers, I used extra vanilla, which was good. Next time, though, I think I would use more chocolate and less sugar - I would have liked it to be richer and more chocolatey, but not necessarily sweeter. I would also try doubling it, because I didn't really like the fact that it's so thin - I wasn't expecting a full-fledged brownie, but my torte was less than 1/4"" thick! Overall, though, a good quick weeknight dessert.

